Contains abstract interfaces for attributes of ARIA roles.

Package net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.aria.attribute Description

Contains abstract interfaces for attributes of ARIA roles.

Client UI API ARIA Attribute

This package contains interfaces for attributes (states and properties) of ARIA roles.
